OL,3,C'Biggest clean-up in a decade'
OL,4,Cunderway on River Thames
OL,6,FMore than 50 abandoned boats have been
OL,7,Frecovered from the River Thames, as
OL,8,Fpart of an Environment Agency (EA)
OL,9,Fcrackdown.
OL,11,FA new task force is working on the
OL,12,F'biggest tidy up in a decade' across
OL,13,Fthe non-tidal Thames.
OL,15,FIt includes removing old and discarded
OL,16,Fboats as well as those that are
OL,17,Funregistered or left at unauthorised
OL,18,Fmoorings.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
