PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773411078
OL,3,C'Biggest clean-up in a decade'
OL,4,Cunderway on River Thames
OL,6,FThe EA is aiming to remove more than
OL,7,F100 vessels by the end of March 2026,
OL,8,Fin a bid to improve the waterway.
OL,10,FEnvironment Agency Navigation
OL,11,FOperations Deputy Director Bill
OL,12,FJephson said: "Irresponsible boat
OL,13,Fowners have caused a blight on the
OL,14,FThames for far too long.
OL,16,F"We know the impact these boats can
OL,17,Fhave on river users and local
OL,18,Fresidents.
OL,26,@tD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773411078
OL,3,C'Biggest clean-up in a decade'
OL,4,Cunderway on River Thames
OL,6,F"It's time to start with a clean
OL,7,Fslate. Sunk, wrecked or abandoned,
OL,8,Fthey've got to go."
OL,10,FIt is the boat owner's responsibility
OL,11,Fto remove their sunken wrecks and
OL,12,Fwhere owners can be identified, the
OL,13,FEnvironment Agency said it will look
OL,14,Fto recover costs.
OL,16,FMr Jephson continued: "Our approach to
OL,17,Fnon-registration offences on the
OL,18,FThames has also changed.
OL,26,@pD@SO]xD@WOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773411078
OL,3,C'Biggest clean-up in a decade'
OL,4,Cunderway on River Thames
OL,6,F"While we continue to prosecute
OL,7,Foffenders through our escalation
OL,8,Fprocess, we have also begun to remove
OL,9,Fboats where the owner has previously
OL,10,Fbeen prosecuted and continues not to
OL,11,Fcomply.
OL,13,F"We are currently recruiting more
OL,14,Fpatrol officers to clamp down further.
OL,15,FIt's time to put pride back into the
OL,16,Friver."
OL,26,@xD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
