PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773411078
OL,3,C'Biggest clean-up in a decade'
OL,4,Cunderway on River Thames
OL,6,FThe task force was established in July
OL,7,F2025 and it removed 35 boats from the
OL,8,FLower Thames over a few days of
OL,9,Fintensive action in September 2025 and
OL,10,Fa further 18 this January.
OL,12,FWhile some boats canbe towed away,
OL,13,Fsunken vessels often need to be lifted
OL,14,Fout the water using flotation bags and
OL,15,Fthen have any water pumped out before
OL,16,Fbeing removed.
OL,18,FOnce recovered, the abandoned boats
OL,19,Fare taken to the Environment Agency's
OL,20,Fdepot at Caversham Lakes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
