PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773411078
OL,3,C'Biggest clean-up in a decade'
OL,4,Cunderway on River Thames
OL,6,FIf they are assessed to be of any
OL,7,Fmonetary value, they are sold at
OL,8,Fauction with proceeds invested back
OL,9,Finto the waterways.
OL,11,FAny boats that aren't salvageable are
OL,12,Fdestroyed.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
